OL,6,FFans described how they have "never
OL,7,Ffelt so scared in my life" as Doyle's
OL,8,FFord Galaxy ` which weighed nearly two
OL,9,Ftonnes ` collided with "well over 100
OL,10,Fpeople" in the space of two minutes.
OL,12,FJailing him Judge Andrew Menary KC,
OL,13,Fsaid Doyle "shouted expressions of
OL,14,Ffrustration underline your state of
OL,15,Fmind at the time, not fear or panic
OL,16,Fbut an inexplicable and undiluted
OL,17,Ffury".
