OL,6,F"To drive a vehicle into crowds of
OL,7,Fpedestrians with such persistence and
OL,8,Fdisregard for human life defies
OL,9,Fordinary understanding."
OL,11,FThe judge added: "Your actions caused
OL,12,Fhorror and devastation on a scale not
OL,13,Fpreviously encountered by this court."
OL,15,FDoyle admitted dangerous driving,
OL,16,Faffray, 17 charges of attempting to
OL,17,Fcause grievous bodily harm (GBH) with
OL,18,Fintent, nine counts of causing GBH
OL,19,Fwith intent and three counts of
OL,20,Fwounding with intent last month.
