OL,6,FHe had previously denied the offences,
OL,7,Fwhich relate to 29 victims aged
OL,8,Fbetween six months and 77 years.
OL,10,FContinuing his sentencing remarks
OL,11,FJudge Menary told Doyle he "lost his
OL,12,Ftemper in a rage, determined to force
OL,13,Fyour way through the crowd regardless
OL,14,Fof the consequences".
OL,16,F"From the outset your driving was
OL,17,Faggressive and dangerous you
OL,18,Ffrightened pedestrians leaning on your
OL,19,Fhorn and shouting obscenities," he
OL,20,Fsaid.
