OL,6,F"You made the conscious choice to
OL,7,Fdrive past the cones and into the
OL,8,Fheart of the crowd...
OL,10,F"Between 5.59 and 6.01pm, a mere two
OL,11,Fminutes, you used your vehicle in a
OL,12,Fmanner that turned it into a weapon,
OL,13,Fdriving deliberately into and over
OL,14,Fmore than 100 people on Dale Street
OL,15,Fand Water Street.
OL,17,F"You paused twice during this rampage,
OL,18,Feach time you could have stopped, but
OL,19,Fyou chose to continue, revving the
OL,20,Fengine and ignoring the screams and
OL,21,Fchaos around you.
