OL,6,F"The footage is truly shocking, it is
OL,7,Fdifficult, if not impossible, to
OL,8,Fconvey in words alone the scene of
OL,9,Fdevastation you caused.
OL,11,F"It shows you quite deliberately
OL,12,Faccelerating into groups of fans time
OL,13,Fand time again, you struck people head
OL,14,Fon, knocked others onto the bonnet,
OL,15,Fdrove over limbs, crushed prams and
OL,16,Fforced those nearby to scatter in
OL,17,Fterror.
