OL,6,FPedestrians pulled their children out
OL,7,Fof the path of Doyle's car to stop
OL,8,Fthem from being hit, and the footage
OL,9,Fshowed the windscreen smash after a
OL,10,Fman landed on it.
OL,12,FFollowing the rampage, Doyle told
OL,13,Fofficers in the back of a police van:
OL,14,F"I've just ruined my family's life."
OL,16,FReferring to the time period between
OL,17,F5.59pm and 6.01pm prosecutor MR
OL,18,FGreaney KC said: "The prosecution case
OL,19,Fis that the defendant had used the
OL,20,Fvehicle as a weapon over that period
OL,21,Fof time.
